nfcchat (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * UI to configure connection settings.
  * Support for connectionless LLCP mode.

 -- Andreas Jakl <>  Mon, 26 Sep 2011 14:10:49 +0300

nfcchat (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * 1.3.1: Updates related to the documentation.
  * 1.3.0: Corrected LLCP URI according to NFC standards.
  * 1.3.0: Text wrapping in the view.
  * 1.2.0: Option to choose whether to send outgoing messages through the server or the client socket.
  * 1.1.0: Ported UI to Qt Quick Components.
  * 1.1.0: Added MeeGo Harmattan support.
  * 1.1.0: Symbian: added NFC availability check, incorporating the NFC Settings App
  * 1.0.0: First version

 -- Andreas Jakl <>  Mon, 25 Jul 2011 13:35:05 +0300
